# Useful Commands

Restart Django

```
sudo systemctl restart recruiter
```

View logs

```
sudo journalctl -u recruiter -f
```

Restart Nginx

```
sudo systemctl restart nginx
```

Reload Nginx

```
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

Check configuration

```
sudo nginx -t
```

Find sockets

```
find /run -name "*.sock"
```

View listening ports

```
sudo ss -tlnp
```

Test socket

```
curl --unix-socket /run/recruiter/gunicorn.sock http://localhost/
```

View loaded Nginx configuration

```
sudo nginx -T
```

