# Deployment Checklist

* Django application works locally.
* Virtual environment created.
* Gunicorn installed.
* Gunicorn starts successfully.
* systemd service is active.
* Socket created.
* Socket responds to curl.
* Nginx configuration passes validation.
* Nginx serves the application locally.
* DNS points to the server.
* SSL certificate installed.
* Ports 80 and 443 are open in both UFW and the AWS Security Group.
* Cloudflare (if used) is set to **Full (strict)** after the certificate is installed.
